query:
SELECT 
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM articles) as total,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM articles WHERE content LIKE '%numbered-teaser%' OR content LIKE '%widget__%' OR content LIKE '%border-radius%' OR content LIKE '%font-size:%' OR content LIKE '%display:flex%' OR content LIKE '%background-color%' OR content LIKE '%counter-increment%') as css_junk,
  (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM articles WHERE content NOT LIKE '%numbered-teaser%' AND content NOT LIKE '%widget__%' AND content NOT LIKE '%border-radius%' AND content NOT LIKE '%font-size:%' AND content NOT LIKE '%display:flex%' AND content NOT LIKE '%background-color%' AND content NOT LIKE '%counter-increment%') as clean;
